<i>adverb</i>: 섭섭히 [섭써피] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>섭섭히 [섭써피]</dt><br>
<dd>1. regrettably</dd><br>
<dd>서운하고 아쉽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a sorry and sad feeling.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sadly</dd><br>
<dd>없어지는 것이 슬프고 아깝게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a sad and sorry feeling about someone or something disappearing.</dd><br>
<dd>3. disappointedly</dd><br>
<dd>기대에 어긋나 서운하거나 불만스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Sorry and dissatisfied because something fails to meet one's expectations.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>